# Python Automation Lab

A growing collection of Python automation tools, experiments,
and engineering workflows focused on:

- PDF/data processing
- filesystem automation
- systems tooling
- CLI utilities
- ETL workflows

## Current Status

This repository is under active development as part of a
broader study of Python automation engineering and internal
tooling development.

